u00e8m v\u0103n ph\u00f2ng gi\u00e1 r\u1ebb m\u1edbi nh\u1ea5t<\/span><br \/>\n<\/strong><\/span><em><span style=\"font-size: 110%;\"><strong>1. R\u00e8m l\u00e1 d\u1ecdc tay k\u00e9o xoay l\u1eadt<\/strong><\/span><\/em><br \/>\n<span style=\"font-size: 95%;\"><a href=\"https:\/\/remphuthanh.com\/danh-muc\/rem-la-doc\/\"><span style=\"color: #0000ff;\">R\u00e8m l\u00e1 d\u1ecdc<\/span><\/a> c\u00f2n c\u00f3 t\u00ean g\u1ecdi kh\u00e1c l\u00e0 &#8220;r\u00e8m l\u00e1 l\u1eadt v\u0103n ph\u00f2ng&#8221;. <span style=\"color: #0000ff;\"><a style=\"color: #0000ff;\" href=\"https:\/\/remphuthanh.com\/danh-muc\/rem-la-doc\/\">R\u00e8m l\u00e1 d\u1ecdc<\/a><\/span> th\u01b0\u1eddng \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c l\u1eafp \u0111\u1eb7t nhi\u1ec1u tr\u00ean nh\u1eefng v\u00e1ch k\u00ednh tr\u00ean nh\u1eefng t\u00f2a v\u0103n ph\u00f2ng. Lo\u1ea1i r\u00e8m n\u00e0y \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c l\u00e0m b\u1eb1ng nh\u1ef1a pha s\u1ee3i t\u1ed5ng h\u1ee3p, \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c c\u1ea5u t\u1ea1o b\u1edfi c\u00e1c l\u00e1 v\u1ea3i d\u1ecdc th\u1ea3 xu\u1ed1ng li\u00ean ti\u1ebfp v\u1edbi nhau \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c li\u00ean k\u1ebft b\u1edfi s\u1ee3i d\u00e2y ch\u1eafc ch\u1eafn, B\u1ea3n l\u00e1 r\u00e8m c\u00f3 \u0111\u1ed9 r\u1ed9ng 8,9cm v\u00e0 12,7cm. R\u00e8m c\u00f3 th\u1ec3 xoay l\u1eadt c\u00e1c l\u00e1 sang tr\u00e1i ho\u1eb7c sang ph\u1ea3i 180 \u0111\u1ed9 hay k\u00e9o d\u1ea1t sang m\u1ed9t b\u00ean ho\u1eb7c 2 b\u00ean n\u00ean vi\u1ec7c \u0111i\u1ec1u ch\u1ec9nh \u00e1nh s\u00e1ng r\u1ea5t linh ho\u1ea1t<\/span><br \/>\n<span style=\"font-size: 95%;\">V\u1edbi ch\u1ea5t li\u1ec7u ch\u1ed1ng tia c\u1ef1c t\u00edm, r\u00e8m l\u00e1 d\u1ecdc c\u00f3 th\u1ec3 c\u00e1ch nhi\u1ec7t, c\u1ea3n n\u1eafng, c\u1ea3n s\u00e1ng hi\u1ec7u qu\u1ea3 \u0111\u1ebfn 95%. Lo\u1ea1i r\u00e8m n\u00e0y kh\u00e1 \u0111a d\u1ea1ng v\u1ec1 m\u00e0u s\u1eafc v\u00e0 m\u1eabu m\u00e3. V\u1edbi \u01b0u \u0111i\u1ec3m l\u00e0 b\u1ec1n, gi\u00e1 r\u1ebb n\u00ean hi\u1ec7n nay n\u00f3 r\u1ea5t \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c \u01b0a chu\u1ed9ng trong kh\u00f4ng gian l\u00e0m vi\u1ec7c<\/span><\/p>\n<p style=\"text-align: center;\"><img decoding=\"async\" loading=\"lazy\" class=\" wp-image-2976 aligncenter\" src=\"https:\/\/remphuthanh.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2020\/02\/rem-la-doc-can-sang-cach-nhiet-533x400.jpg\" alt=\"\" width=\"1326\" height=\"995\" srcset=\"https:\/\/remphuthanh.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2020\/02\/rem-la-doc-can-sang-cach-nhiet-533x400.jpg 533w, https:\/\/remphuthanh.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2020\/02\/rem-la-doc-can-sang-cach-nhiet-510x383.jpg 510w, https:\/\/remphuthanh.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2020\/02\/rem-la-doc-can-sang-cach-nhiet-768x576.jpg 768w, https:\/\/remphuthanh.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2020\/02\/rem-la-doc-can-sang-cach-nhiet.jpg 1024w\" sizes=\"(max-width: 1326px) 100vw, 1326px\" title=\"\"><em><strong>r\u00e8m l\u00e1 d\u1ecdc c\u1ea3n <span style=\"font-size: 14.4px;\">s\u00e1ng c\u00e1ch nhi\u1ec7t\u00a0<\/span><\/strong><span style=\"font-size: 14.4px;\">\u00a0<\/span><\/em><\/p>\n<p><em><strong><span style=\"font-size: 110%;\">2. R\u00e8m cu\u1ed1n v\u0103n ph\u00f2ng \u0111\u1eb9p gi\u00e1 r\u1ebb<\/span><\/strong><\/em><br \/>\n<span style=\"font-size: 95%;\">V\u1edbi thi\u1ebft k\u1ebf \u0111\u01a1n gi\u1ea3n, s\u1eed d\u1ee5ng d\u1ec5 d\u00e0ng nh\u01b0ng to\u00e1t l\u00ean s\u1ef1 sang tr\u1ecdng cho kh\u00f4ng gian l\u00e0m vi\u1ec7c, <a href=\"https:\/\/remphuthanh.com\/danh-muc\/rem-cuon\/\"><span style=\"color: #0000ff;\">R\u00e8m cu\u1ed1n v\u0103n ph\u00f2ng gi\u00e1 r\u1ebb<\/span><\/a> ng\u00e0y c\u00e0ng \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c s\u1eed d\u1ee5ng nhi\u1ec1u. Kh\u00f4ng ch\u1ec9 c\u00f3 t\u00ednh th\u1ea9m m\u1ef9 m\u00e0 n\u00f3 c\u00f2n gi\u00fap cho kh\u00f4ng gian n\u01a1i \u0111\u00e2y tr\u1edf n\u00ean tho\u00e1ng m\u00e1t, t\u1ea1o hi\u1ec7u qu\u1ea3 l\u00e0m vi\u1ec7c t\u1ed1t h\u01a1n cho nh\u00e2n vi\u00ean<\/span><\/p>\n<p style=\"text-align: center;\"><img decoding=\"async\" loading=\"lazy\" class=\" wp-image-2979 aligncenter\" src=\"https:\/\/remphuthanh.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2020\/02\/rem-cuon-van-phong-dep-592x400.jpg\" alt=\"\" width=\"1330\" height=\"899\" srcset=\"https:\/\/remphuthanh.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2020\/02\/rem-cuon-van-phong-dep-592x400.jpg 592w, https:\/\/remphuthanh.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2020\/02\/rem-cuon-van-phong-dep-510x345.jpg 510w, https:\/\/remphuthanh.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2020\/02\/rem-cuon-van-phong-dep-768x519.jpg 768w, https:\/\/remphuthanh.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2020\/02\/rem-cuon-van-phong-dep.jpg 1024w\" sizes=\"(max-width: 1330px) 100vw, 1330px\" title=\"\"><strong><em>r\u00e8m cu\u1ed1n v\u0103n ph\u00f2ng gi\u00e1 r\u1ebb nhi\u1ec1u c\u00f4ng n\u0103ng<\/em><\/strong><\/p>\n<p>Ch\u1ea5t li\u1ec7u lo\u1ea1i r\u00e8m n\u00e0y c\u0169ng kh\u00e1c ho\u00e0n to\u00e0n so v\u1edbi r\u00e8m c\u1eeda th\u00f4ng th\u01b0\u1eddng m\u00e0 ch\u00fang ta v\u1eabn s\u1eed d\u1ee5ng. N\u00f3 c\u00f3 th\u1ec3 l\u00e0 v\u1ea3i d\u1ec7t, c\u00f3 th\u1ec3 l\u00e0 nh\u1ef1a ph\u1ee7 b\u00f3ng,&#8230; \u0111\u1ec3 c\u00f3 th\u1ec3 ph\u1ee5c v\u1ee5 c\u0169ng nh\u01b0 \u0111\u00e1p \u1ee9ng m\u1ecdi ti\u00eau ch\u00ed, y\u00eau c\u1ea7u kh\u1eaft khe nh\u1ea5t c\u1ee7a kh\u00e1ch h\u00e0ng. V\u1edbi c\u01a1 ch\u1ebf ho\u1ea1t \u0111\u1ed9ng l\u00e0 k\u00e9o l\u00ean, th\u1ea3 xu\u1ed1ng, \u0111i\u1ec1u khi\u1ec3n 1 d\u00e2y k\u00e9o. C\u00f3 th\u1ec3 k\u00e9o l\u00ean xu\u1ed1ng \u1edf nhi\u1ec1u \u0111\u1ed9, gi\u00fap b\u1ea1n d\u1ec5 d\u00e0ng \u0111i\u1ec1u ch\u1ec9nh m\u1ee9c \u0111\u1ed9 \u00e1nh s\u00e1ng cho c\u0103n ph\u00f2ng. Vi\u1ec7c v\u1ec7 sinh c\u0169ng tr\u1edf n\u00ean \u0111\u01a1n gi\u1ea3n v\u00e0 d\u1ec5 d\u00e0ng h\u01a1n m\u1ed7i khi b\u1ea1n mu\u1ed1n lau ch\u00f9i b\u1ee5i b\u1ea9n sau m\u1ed9t th\u1eddi gian s\u1eed d\u1ee5ng<\/p>\n<p style=\"text-align: center;\"><img decoding=\"async\" loading=\"lazy\" class=\" wp-image-2980 aligncenter\" src=\"https:\/\/remphuthanh.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2020\/02\/rem-cuon-van-phong-dep-1-576x400.jpg\" alt=\"\" width=\"1321\" height=\"917\" srcset=\"https:\/\/remphuthanh.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2020\/02\/rem-cuon-van-phong-dep-1-576x400.jpg 576w, https:\/\/remphuthanh.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2020\/02\/rem-cuon-van-phong-dep-1-510x354.jpg 510w, https:\/\/remphuthanh.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2020\/02\/rem-cuon-van-phong-dep-1-768x533.jpg 768w, https:\/\/remphuthanh.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2020\/02\/rem-cuon-van-phong-dep-1.jpg 900w\" sizes=\"(max-width: 1321px) 100vw, 1321px\" title=\"\"><strong><em>r\u00e8m cu\u1ed1n v\u0103n ph\u00f2ng gi\u00e1 r\u1ebb g\u1ecdn nh\u1eb9, d\u1ec5 d\u00e0ng s\u1eed d\u1ee5ng, d\u1ec5 v\u1ec7 sinh<\/em><\/strong><\/p>\n<p><strong><em><span style=\"font-size: 120%;\">3. R\u00e8m s\u00e1o nh\u00f4m v\u0103n ph\u00f2ng<\/span><\/em><\/strong><br \/>\n<span style=\"font-size: 95%;\"><a href=\"https:\/\/remphuthanh.com\/danh-muc\/rem-sao-nhom\/\"><span style=\"color: #0000ff;\">R\u00e8m s\u00e1o nh\u00f4m<\/span><\/a> hay c\u00f2n g\u1ecdi l\u00e0 m\u00e0nh s\u00e1o nh\u00f4m, \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c l\u00e0m t\u1eeb nh\u1eefng l\u00e1 nh\u00f4m d\u00e1t c\u1ef1c m\u1ecfng c\u00f3 b\u1ea3n r\u1ed9ng 2,5cm. <span style=\"color: #0000ff;\"><a style=\"color: #0000ff;\" href=\"https:\/\/remphuthanh.com\/danh-muc\/rem-sao-nhom\/\">R\u00e8m s\u00e1o nh\u00f4m<\/a><\/span> \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c thi\u1ebft k\u1ebf h\u1ebft s\u1ee9c \u0111\u01a1n gi\u1ea3n v\u00e0 d\u1ec5 d\u00e0ng s\u1eed d\u1ee5ng, b\u1ea3o d\u01b0\u1ee1ng, c\u00f3 th\u1ec3 xoay l\u1eadt 180 \u0111\u1ed9 \u0111\u1ec3 \u0111i\u1ec1u ch\u1ec9nh \u00e1nh s\u00e1ng theo y mu\u1ed1n. C\u00e1c l\u00e1 nh\u00f4m \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c s\u01a1n m\u00e0u t\u0129nh \u0111i\u1ec7n, m\u00e0u s\u1eafc t\u01b0\u01a1i s\u00e1ng, \u0111a d\u1ea1ng, c\u1ea3n s\u00e1ng 100% ch\u1ed1ng n\u1eafng l\u00ean \u0111\u1ebfn 80%<\/span><\/p>\n<p style=\"text-align: center;\"><img decoding=\"async\" loading=\"lazy\" class=\" wp-image-2981 aligncenter\" src=\"https:\/\/remphuthanh.com\/wp-con