a1o s\u1ef1 m\u1ec1m m\u1ea1i cho b\u1ea3n l\u00e1 nh\u00f4m<\/span><\/p>\n<p><img decoding=\"async\" loading=\"lazy\" class=\" wp-image-2982 aligncenter\" src=\"https:\/\/remphuthanh.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2020\/02\/rem-sao-nhom-cho-van-phong-1-400x400.jpg\" alt=\"\" width=\"1267\" height=\"1267\" srcset=\"https:\/\/remphuthanh.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2020\/02\/rem-sao-nhom-cho-van-phong-1-400x400.jpg 400w, https:\/\/remphuthanh.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2020\/02\/rem-sao-nhom-cho-van-phong-1-510x510.jpg 510w, https:\/\/remphuthanh.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2020\/02\/rem-sao-nhom-cho-van-phong-1-280x280.jpg 280w, https:\/\/remphuthanh.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2020\/02\/rem-sao-nhom-cho-van-phong-1-768x768.jpg 768w, https:\/\/remphuthanh.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2020\/02\/rem-sao-nhom-cho-van-phong-1-800x800.jpg 800w, https:\/\/remphuthanh.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2020\/02\/rem-sao-nhom-cho-van-phong-1-100x100.jpg 100w, https:\/\/remphuthanh.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2020\/02\/rem-sao-nhom-cho-van-phong-1.jpg 900w\" sizes=\"(max-width: 1267px) 100vw, 1267px\" title=\"\"><\/p>\n<p style=\"text-align: left;\"><strong><em><span style=\"font-size: 120%;\">4. R\u00e8m s\u00e1o g\u1ed7 cho v\u0103n ph\u00f2ng<\/span><\/em><\/strong><br \/>\n<span style=\"font-size: 95%;\"><a href=\"https:\/\/remphuthanh.com\/danh-muc\/rem-sao-go\/\"><span style=\"color: #0000ff;\">R\u00e8m s\u00e1o g\u1ed7<\/span><\/a> l\u00e0 s\u1ea3n ph\u1ea9m r\u00e8m c\u1eeda \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c l\u00e0m b\u1eb1ng g\u1ed7 t\u1ef1 nhi\u00ean 100%. R\u00e8m g\u1ed7 l\u00e0 s\u1ea3n ph\u1ea9m c\u1ee7a s\u1ef1 s\u00e1ng t\u1ea1o, tinh t\u1ebf, th\u1ec3 hi\u1ec7n phong c\u00e1ch hi\u1ec7n \u0111\u1ea1i \u0111\u1eb3ng c\u1ea5p nh\u01b0ng v\u1eabn mang v\u1ebb \u0111\u1eb9p th\u00e2n thi\u1ec7n \u1ea5m \u00e1p c\u1ee7a thi\u00ean nhi\u00ean<\/span><br \/>\n<span style=\"font-size: 95%;\">R\u00e8m g\u1ed7 \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c l\u00e0m b\u1eb1ng g\u1ed7 t\u1ef1 nhi\u00ean n\u00ean g\u1ed7 r\u1ea5t ti\u1